<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA3">
<l>avarkkē yeḻupiṟappu māḷāvō meṉṟu</l>
<l>mavarkkēnā maṉpāva tallāṟ - pavarccaṭaimēṟ</l>
<l>pākappōḻ cūṭu mavarkkallāṉ maṟṟoruvark</l>
<l>kākāppō meññāṉṟu māḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Besides we becoming love for him, saying</l>
<l>“we shall be servants of him alone for seven birth”, except to him</l>
<l>who wears a partial piece on his dense matted hair</l>
<l>we shall never be servants to anyone.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
